Once processed, telemetry can be analyzed by AI systems.

ML Models

Structured prediction:

sleep scoring,

arrhythmia detection,

activity recognition.


Deep Learning

Complex pattern analysis:

voice emotion detection,

EEG classification,

movement prediction.


LLMs

Language reasoning:

summarizing trends,

generating reports,

coding agents,

research assistance.


Example:

Telemetry
   ↓
Feature Vector
   ↓
AI Model
   ↓
LLM Summary


